casebody.data:
PEOPLE of the State of Michigan, Plaintiff-Appellee,
v.
Jonathan CLIFFORD, Defendant-Appellant. SC: 158580
COA: 344691 Supreme Court of Michigan. April 30, 2019

Order

On order of the Court, the application for leave to appeal the August 7, 2018 order of the Court of Appeals is considered, and it is DENIED, because we are not persuaded that the questions presented should be reviewed by this Court. The motions to subpoena the Walker hearing transcript and to admit witness statement are DENIED.
